@startuml
<style>
document {
    BoxPadding 10
    ParticipantPadding 10
}
</style>

actor User
participant "Performance Page" as UI
participant "UserController" as Controller
participant "UserService" as Service
participant "TaskRepository" as TaskRepository
database MongoDB

User -> UI: Chọn bộ lọc xem hiệu suất
activate UI

UI -> Controller: Call API Get User Performance
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: getPerformance(userId, query)
activate Service

Service -> Service: getUserPerformancePipeline(userId, query)

Service -> TaskRepository: aggregate(pipeline)
activate TaskRepository

TaskRepository -> MongoDB: aggregate(pipeline)
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> TaskRepository: aggregationResult
deactivate MongoDB

TaskRepository --> Service: aggregationResult
deactivate TaskRepository

Service -> Service: Calculate KPIs, Completion Rate & Map DTO Data

Service --> Controller: UserPerformanceDto
deactivate Service

Controller --> UI: Trả về dữ liệu hiệu suất (200 OK)
deactivate Controller

UI --> User: Hiển thị biểu đồ tiến độ và hiệu suất làm việc
deactivate UI

@enduml